	   (semantic-tag-class (semantic-current-tag))
		'(function variable))
    (error "The cursor must be in a function or class variable to get the callers"))
  (jdee-xref-class-and-token-to-signature
   (jdee-xref-get-current-class)
   (semantic-current-tag)))

